I->Main
You->Tum
He/She->Wo
we->Hum
They->Wo Sab


Practical Present Tense
Subject + Verb(Base Form)

Past Tense
Subject + Verb(Past Form)

Future Tense
Subject + Will + Verb
I Will Try To Speak English


Present Tense ->Verb Rule
I/You/We/They + Verb(base form)
He/she + Verb + s
I-Am
He/She/Name-is
You->are
we->are
They->are
Negative Questions->I/you/we/They->Do-->Don't
                    He/She->Does->Doesn't


Past Tense->Verb Rule
I/You/We/They + Verb(base form)
He/she
I->Was
He/She/Name->Was
You->were
we->were
They->were
Negative Questions->I/you/we/They ->Did -didn't
                    He/She

Future Tense->verb Rule Is Also Same
I/You/We/They He/she->will be

Negative Questions->I/you/we/They-will -> will not
                    He/She-will 





